{"ts":"2026-07-06T21:24:55.022Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-dfg0"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Cursor pagination and bounded-output defaults for list/search/context at scale"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Bounded-output child of pm-9rxu: unbounded listings are token-catastrophic at 100k+ items. Related (not duplicate): pm-cfed lean JSON and pm-alnj search --limit shape single payloads; this defines the paging contract across read commands."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","area:sdk","scale"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:24:55.022Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:24:55.022Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":480},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"list/search/context accept a stable cursor (--after/--cursor per ADR contract) with deterministic ordering; at-scale default limits keep any single invocation under a documented token budget with an explicit truncation marker + next-cursor hint; small workspaces see no behavior change; contracts/MCP/completions/docs regenerated"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-9rxu"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"medium"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-bl8x","kind":"blocked_by","created_at":"2026-07-06T21:24:55.022Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"1f78e8f37ddc4c227e2c80dd9d658e5f327dc2357f74d06e2a21b090de353cf9","message":""}
{"ts":"2026-07-10T21:40:37.369Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"note_add","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-10T21:40:37.369Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/notes","value":[{"created_at":"2026-07-10T21:40:37.369Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Wave-2 chain scoping 2026-07-10 (planning pass). This item is the sole blocker of pm-55ra (token-budget context packer) and thus gates the wave-2 tail; it is itself blocked by ADR pm-bl8x decision point 3 (cursor vs offset). Current surface (verified in code): pm list has --limit/--offset with NO default bound (list.ts:352-409, total emitted only when paginating); pm search has --limit only (search.ts:383/2608), no offset, no cursor; pm context defaults DEFAULT_CONTEXT_LIMIT=10 but --depth full lifts it to MAX_SAFE_INTEGER (context.ts:313/418) — the one truly unbounded default hole. No cursor token exists anywhere. Suggested slices: S1 cursor primitive in the SDK read/query layer shipped by pm-rjqr — opaque cursor encoding a stable sort tuple (sort key + id tiebreak), envelope gains next_cursor/has_more; this is ADR-input work and can start as a spike BEFORE pm-bl8x formally lands (recommend cursor-over-offset to the ADR, offset degrades at 100k+). S2 pm list adoption — threshold-gated default limit (small workspaces keep today's unbounded behavior per pm-z436 small-end concerns; large workspaces get a bounded default + next_cursor), --offset retained as compat alias. S3 pm search adoption — ranked-result cursors are rank-stability-sensitive (BM25/semantic scores shift between invocations); options: snapshot cursor (embed result-id window) vs re-rank-and-skip; decide in S3, not S1. S4 pm context/next bounded degradation — close the --depth full hole and hand off to pm-55ra, whose packer consumes S1 primitives for budget-aware truncation. Coordination: pm-9rxu (scale epic parent), pm-rjqr (S1 lands in its query facade), pm-3mna/pm-usfg promotion wave (S1 belongs in SDK not CLI per SDK-first), pm-z436 (threshold defaults), pm-gdi7/pm-nilh (envelope verbosity — next_cursor must not bloat lean output)."}]}],"before_hash":"1f78e8f37ddc4c227e2c80dd9d658e5f327dc2357f74d06e2a21b090de353cf9","after_hash":"fd373413a2961ae64509090522dc831d706ff3ce0d0e544db088eb9e9a883a27"}
